             was indicted for <rs id="t17821204-23-off115" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17821204-23-off115" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17821204-23-off115" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17821204-23-cd116" type="crimeDate">26th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821204-23-off115 t17821204-23-cd116"></join> last one linen sheet, value 2 s. one pair of linen check bed curtains, value 3 s. and one feather bed, value 20 s. the goods of 
                     <persName id="t17821204-23-victim281" type="victimName">
                        Carey 
                        Emms
                     <interp inst="t17821204-23-victim281" type="surname" value="Emms"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17821204-23-victim281" type="given" value="Carey"></interp>
